#483
Before the Castle~
You are standing atop a huge staircase, stretching down hundreds of feet to
the City of Medievia.  This landing is on the edge of a giant island in
the sky.  In front of you is a magnificent castle, made of silvery-white
stone, gleaming in the sunlight.  It has many high towers and spires of
various heights.  A wide dirt road leads north to the castle's drawbridge.
