#804
Standing On A Ledge~
Digging your finger tips into the spaces between the stone blocks of the
castle wall, and standing on your tip toes on the narrow ledge, you cling
dangerously high above the ground.  Looking back over your shoulder, you can
see the castle's moat far below.  You hold your breath and make a silent
prayer to the gods as you inch your way along the protruding ledge.  It
continues to the west and meets a large balcony to the east.
