#896
The Private Library~
All four walls of this chamber are lined with wooden book cases. Their
shelves strained under the weight of thousands of different kinds of books.
Some appear to be mundane but most have been kept in pristine condition
and are covered with golden binding, obviously the spell books of Vryce.
A square table rests in the center of the room with a large, glowing orb
hovering above it, illuminating the entire room. A padded leather chair
is pushed in under the ornately carved stone table.
