#955
A Meeting Chamber~
In the middle of the west wall an elaborate fireplace is flanked by the carved
effigies of lions which form the sides of the mantle.  Above the fire, a wall
hanging depicts a gold dragon within a pentacle design.  On the right side
of the fireplace hangs a large leash of black varnished leather, inset with
small diamonds and golden studs.  A low table in front of the fire is
accompanied by three large chairs forming a semicircle around this hearth.
In the middle of the room is a larger table with an oversized silver dish.
The silver platter holds several delicious pieces of ripe fruit.  In the
southwest corner a steep and narrow staircase leads up into the darkness of
the ceiling vault, fifteen feet above the floor.  In the center of the east
wall is a spiral staircase leading down.  There is a computer here.
~
