#986
A Black Tiled Path~
You are standing in an enormous room.  The walls stretch far out in each
direction and the ceiling is lost in the shadows.  The floor here is tiled
with smooth, glass-like black rocks, so pure of color that it almost appears
you were levitating over a void.  Looking to the east and west, you are
completely amazed by what you see.  Off the path to the east is a small forest
and to the west the floor is completely gone, just air and clouds hover in
the empty space of the chamber.
