#1154
The Audience Chamber~
This is a large, open room with a high domed ceiling. Ancient tapestries
of superb artistic design hang on the walls depicting the history of Medievia.
The ceiling is made of colored glass, showing in great detail, a huge gold
dragon. A magical light shines behind the glass, bathing the room in a soft
glow. The only furnishings are a circular table made of wood in the center
of the room, measuring at least twenty feet in diameter; and many chairs
with comfortable padding on the seats arranged around the table.
