#1163
A Majestic Stone Corridor~
This is an enormous hallway, more than fifteen feet wide and at least twenty
feet high. The walls and ceiling are made of polished, charcoal colored
granite. The floor tiles are hexagon shaped and made from a dull silver
stone. Platinum chains hang from the ceiling, about five feet, with large
spheres of flame attached to the end, burning brightly. The magical flames
produce no smoke and brightly illuminate the passageway. The air is musty
and irritates your lungs as your movement stirs up dust. You have an eerie
feeling about this place as a chill runs up your spine.
~
