#2072
A Large Balcony~
You are on a large balcony, extending from the front of Castle Medievia.
The floor is made of white marble tiles and has been kept clean and new
looking, despite the weather and passage of time. A waist high railing
surrounds this semi-circular platform, also made of white marble. The
posts are ornately carved as are the banisters sides, with a wide, flat
top. Looking out, you see a stunning view of the castle courtyard and
surrounding floating island. Further out, you can see the entire city of
Medievia as well as the countryside stretched out before you.  Decorative
ivy is growing along the wall above you, reaching upwards.
