#3565
Tip of a Spire~
You stand atop a tall, round tower protruding from the castle's roof.  A
small, waist-high wall surrounds this circular landing.  You can see the
vast, majestic lands of Medievia in all directions from here.  A light
breeze blows through your hair as you stare a few moments in awe at the
inspiring landscape.  A few hundred feet to the west, at the corner of the
castle, are two spires, reaching even farther into the sky than this one.
A large, circular hole leads down inside this tower.
